111
00:09:20,190 --> 00:09:21,390
su ono što on danas

112
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:22,430
naziva nevolja.

113
00:09:23,410 --> 00:09:25,070
Ovo je zadnje svjedočanstvo,

114
00:09:25,410 --> 00:09:27,030
ali ja hoću da vi razumijete

115
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:29,950
da je otac u kontroli.

116
00:09:31,530 --> 00:09:31,870
Znate,

117
00:09:32,090 --> 00:09:33,230
ne može

118
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:36,070
nitko ništa

119
00:09:36,070 --> 00:09:37,710
bez da on

120
00:09:37,710 --> 00:09:39,430
za to ne zna

121
00:09:39,430 --> 00:09:41,190
ili da amenuje,

122
00:09:41,470 --> 00:09:42,510
bilo da je direktna

123
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:45,650
volja dobro ili dopuštenje zlog,

124
00:09:45,650 --> 00:09:47,690
kroz koje će onda proizaći

125
00:09:47,690 --> 00:09:48,190
veće dobro.

126
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:51,550
I prema tome ona se sad prirodno

127
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:54,070
gledano našla u nezavidnoj situaciji

128
00:09:54,070 --> 00:09:56,570
zato što je i karijera u opasnosti

129
00:09:56,570 --> 00:09:57,870
i sad razmišlja

130
