izabrao. Molim vas

169
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:26,170
da uočite,

170
00:11:26,470 --> 00:11:28,650
ovo je sad Lester Summral

171
00:11:28,650 --> 00:11:31,030
rekao, da je vjera

172
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:32,170
izbor.

173
00:11:33,690 --> 00:11:34,830
Ti ćeš

174
00:11:34,830 --> 00:11:36,990
dokazat da li si

175
