vjernik, time

176
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:41,040
pravednik, ili nevjernik

177
00:11:41,390 --> 00:11:42,890
i nepravednik

178
00:11:42,890 --> 00:11:44,390
svojim izborima.

179
00:11:45,130 --> 00:11:45,990
Odabirima.

180
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:47,990
Odbio

181
