s plaćom,

194
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:25,110
s pozicijom.

195
00:12:34,410 --> 00:12:35,450
Radije je

196
00:12:35,450 --> 00:12:36,050
izabrao

197
00:12:38,470 --> 00:12:39,290
bit

198
