zlostavljan

199
00:12:41,690 --> 00:12:43,250
zajedno s

200
00:12:43,250 --> 00:12:44,550
pukom Božjim.

201
00:12:46,930 --> 00:12:47,690
Jer ti kad si

202
00:12:47,690 --> 00:12:49,970
otvoreno vjernik

203
00:12:49,970 --> 00:12:52,070
i svjedok za Krista, ti si

204
00:12:52,070 --> 00:12:53,750
u direktnom neprijateljstvu

205
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:56,150
sa svijetom koji je sav pod

206
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:58,190
zlim, po 1. Ivanovoj

207
00:12:58,190 --> 00:12:58,830
5:19.

208
00:12:58,830 --> 00:13:00,710
I onime koji

209
00:13:00,710 --> 00:13:02,270
je gospodar ovog svijeta,

210
00:13:02,690 --> 00:13:04,330
jer mu više ne želiš služiti.

211
00:13:04,930 --> 00:13:06,390
To jest poklonit mu se,

212
00:13:06,910 --> 00:13:08,370
a to je što on traži

213
00:13:08,370 --> 00:13:10,990
od tebe.  I pazi,

214
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:14,510
radije je izabrao

215
00:13:15,430 --> 00:13:16,270
bit

216
00:13:16,830 --> 00:13:18,830
zlostavljan zajedno

217
00:13:18,830 --> 00:13:20,430
s pukom Božjim,

218
00:13:21,250 --> 00:13:22,830
nego imat časovito

219
00:13:24,170 --> 00:13:25,010
grješno

220
00:13:25,010 --> 00:13:25,690
uživanje.

221
